# Watchdog alarm log — production log on the droplet writes to
# /var/log/tinyassets/uptime_alarms.log (see scripts/watchdog.py +
# deploy/tinyassets-watchdog.service `LogsDirectory=workflow`). The
# repo-relative path is test-only and must not be tracked. Audit:
# docs/audits/2026-04-26-restart-loop-correlation.md.
.agents/uptime_alarms.log

