.cowork-bootstrap/

# Fundraising / company material. This repo is PUBLIC — a cap table, an
# investor pipeline, and pitch decks must never land in it. Ignored so the
# exclusion is a recorded decision rather than an accident of nobody having
# run `git add` yet. These files are NOT backed up by being ignored — see
# docs/audits/2026-07-22-untracked-business-material.md for the durable-storage
# host ask, and note `git clean -xdff` targets ignored files specifically.
data-room/
pitch-deck/
investor-list/
